<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <h3>Hello <%= @debate.challenger.profile.display_name %>,</h3>
  <p>
  You've received a new debate invitation on <b> Citizen Debate</b>!
  </p>
  <p> <%= @debate.creator.profile.display_name %> has challenged you to debate them on the topic below. You've been challenged to defend the <b> <%= @challenger_side %> </b> of the debate.
  </p>
  <h3><%=@debate.topic.title%> </h3>
  <p>
    To accept this challenge, please simply login via the link below. You can accept this debate challenge and any others by visiting the <a href="www.citizendebate.org/debates">Debates</a> page and viewing your "Pending Debate Challenges" in your account.
  </p>
  <a href="www.citizendebate.org/debates" class="btn btn-default"> Accept Challenge: <%=@debate.topic.title%> </a>

<p>Additionally, if your are interested in providing feedback during our early adopter program, please follow the link below to join our Slack channel.</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="http://bit.ly/citizen-debate-slack">http://bit.ly/citizen-debate-slack </a></li>
</ul>

  <p>Thanks for debating!</p>
</body>
</html>
